Thanks to Demi. Here is the final code:

// Render opaque objects
        [_scene render:renderer opaque:true];

        // First planar shadow pass (if needed)
        [self renderPlanarShadows:renderer];

        // Render transparent objects
        glColorMask(1, 1, 1, 0);
